the claim, the property, or myself.
> Any phone transcripts that include =E2=80=9CC90306048=E2=80=9D, =E2=80=9C=
23 Mays Road=E2=80=9D, or =E2=80=9C23 Mays=E2=80=9D.
>=20
>=20
> Notification of privacy breach
>=20
> I would also like to formally notify a potential privacy breach.
> On 10 August 2025, Grant Metson shared my name and mobile number with =
Stephen Walker (ASUR NZ) by email without my consent and without a clear =
business reason. Given that I have since raised concerns about Mr =
Walker=E2=80=99s independence, I believe this disclosure was =
inappropriate and may present a risk to my privacy and safety.
>=20
> Please confirm that this incident will be logged and investigated in =
accordance with Tower=E2=80=99s privacy obligations and the Privacy Act =
2020.
>=20
> Please confirm receipt of this email and advise when I can expect a =
response or update on both the information request and the privacy =
breach notification.
>=20
> Ng=C4=81 mihi,
> Raffaella
